<div>   
<p>     <span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“人工智能术语”诞生在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1956</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，鲜为人知的是</span></span><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">人工智能</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">研究领域的</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第一项工作</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是在</span><span style="font-family: Verdana;">1943</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年；</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“机器学习”术语诞生在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1959</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，鲜为人知的是</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">机器学习</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第一</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个方法的论者早在</span><span style="font-family: Verdana;">1949</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年就发表了。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">40</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代，神经生理学家沃伦·麦卡洛克和数学家沃尔特·皮茨开发了神经元基本模型，将神经网络的概念引入计算机领域，</span></span><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">被认为人工智能</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第一项工作</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">心理学家唐纳德</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·赫布后来在他的《行为组织》一书中，对此进行了编纂和整理，提出了</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">机器学习的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">赫布学习规则。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">【</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛克</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">-</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">皮茨神经元</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">】</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">沃伦</span><span style="font-family: 楷体;">·斯特吉斯·麦卡洛克（Warren Sturgis McCulloch，1898.11.16-1969.9.24）美国神经生理学家和控制论专家，他以某些大脑理论的基础和他对控制论运动的贡献着称。麦卡洛克和沃尔特·皮茨一起创建了基于数学算法的计算模型</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">，</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">其</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">研究</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">包括两给方面</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">，一</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">是</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">侧重于大脑中的生物过程，另一</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">是</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">侧重于神经网络在人工智能中的应用。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">沃尔特</span><span style="font-family: 楷体;">·哈利·皮茨（</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">Walter Harry Pitts，</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">1923.4.23-1969.5.14）是一名逻辑学家，在计算神经科学领域工作。他提出了具有里程碑意义的神经活动和生成过程的理论公式，这些公式影响了不同的领域，如认知科学和心理学、哲学、神经科学、计算机科学、人工神经网络、控制论和人工智能。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 125%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"> </span><img width="473" height="236" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 125%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="color: #0000FF; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图</span><span style="font-family: Verdana;">1 </span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; line-height: 125%; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">沃伦</span>·<span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛奇</span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（</span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">左）</span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; line-height: 125%; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和沃尔特</span>·<span style="font-family: 宋体;">皮茨</span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（</span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">右）</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1942年，皮茨第一次遇见沃伦·麦卡洛克。麦卡洛克拥有哲学和心理学学位，并于1927年获得医学博士学位。他的兴趣</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">广泛，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">从诗歌到工程。在耶鲁工作了近</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">8年后，他搬到了芝加哥的伊利诺伊大学。麦卡洛克和他的妻子卢克·麦卡洛克</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">把当时无家可归的皮茨夫妇带进了他们的家。麦卡洛克成了皮茨的导师。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1943年，神经科学家沃伦·麦卡洛克和逻辑学家沃尔特·皮茨在《数学生物物理学通报 中发表了</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">题为</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经活动内在思想的逻辑演算</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的论文</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参考资料</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">[1]&#125;</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在这篇论文中，麦卡洛</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">克</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和皮茨试图理解大脑如何通过使用许多连接在一起的基本细胞，来产生高度复杂的模式。这些基本的脑细胞被称为神经元（</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">单核细胞趋化蛋白神经元</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">克</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和皮茨在他们的论文中给出了一个高度简化的神经元模型</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">——</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经网络的第一个数学模型</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">后来被称为</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">经元的</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛克</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">-皮茨</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">模型，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">也称</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛克</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">-皮茨神经元</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">简称</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">MCP神经元。</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛克</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">-皮茨神经元</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">对人工神经网络的发展做出了重要贡献，它模拟了生物神经元的关键特征</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛克</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">-皮茨神经元</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">模型的基本思想是</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">其</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">具有真实神经元某些特征的组件</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">真</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">实</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经元有许多</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“兴奋性”的树突输入，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">也</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">有些是</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“抑制性”的。神经元做什么取决于输入的总和。兴奋性输入倾向于使细胞</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发射</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，即传递信号，而抑制性输入则使细胞</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">不</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发射</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。当细胞发出信号时，信号沿着轴突传播，轴突的作用类似于输出线，然后通过轴突终末传递到其他神经元的输入端。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一个神经元模型，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">难以</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">捕捉到</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">真实</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经元的所有特性和行为，但简化而不破坏其行为</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">捕捉到它执行计算的方式。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如下</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是麦库洛</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">克</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">-</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">皮特神经元</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">特征</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">：</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">它们是二进制设备（</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Vi=[0,1]</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">每个神经元都有一个固定的阈值</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;">θ</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经元接收来自兴奋性突触的输入，所有突触都具有相同的权重。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">4.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">抑制性输入对任何兴奋性输入具有绝对否决权。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">5.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在每一个时间步，神经元同时（同步）更新，将加权兴奋性输入相加，如果总和大于或等于阈值</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;">θ</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，并且如果神经元没有收到抑制性输入，则将输出（</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Vi</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）设置为</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">否则设置为</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">0</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">我们可以用</span></span><span style="line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛克</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">-皮茨</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">输出规则来总结这些规则</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">：</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 125%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><img width="305" height="70" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 125%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">或，图示如下：</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 125%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><img width="615" height="190" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"> </span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 125%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="color: #0000FF; line-height: 125%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图</span><span style="font-family: Verdana;">2 </span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经元结构（左）和麦卡洛克</span><span style="font-family: Verdana;">-</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">皮茨神经元（右）示意图</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">它的操作规则是，在时间</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">t</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">时，它观察它的兴奋性输入，并统计出现的兴奋性输入的数量。如果计数等于或大于阈值且抑制输入为零，则在时间</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">t+1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">时，单元输出</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，否则输出</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">0</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">注意，这个规则比你一开始想象的要复杂得多，它确实会导致非常复杂的行为。</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">使用这个</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">规则</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">可以</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">实现布尔逻辑</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">NOT</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">函数和</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">OR</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">或</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">AND</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">函数。使用</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">NOT</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">OR</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">AND</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">组成的网络</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，可以建立</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">XOR</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、加法器、移位寄存器</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">以及执行计算所需的</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">各种</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">内容。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛克和皮茨</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的</span></span><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经元模型在计算机科学中一直非常重要。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">从某种意义上说，大脑是一个非常大的神经网络。它有数十亿个神经元，每个神经元都与成千上万个其他神经元相连。麦卡洛克和皮茨展示了如何通过适当的单核细胞趋化蛋白神经元网络</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">来编码任何逻辑命题。所以理论上，任何可以用电脑完成的事情也可以用单核细胞趋化蛋白神经元网络来完成。麦卡洛克和皮茨还表明，每个单核细胞趋化蛋白神经元网络都编码一些逻辑命题。所以如果大脑是一个神经网络，那么它会编码一些复杂的计算机程序。但是单核细胞趋化蛋白神经元不是真正的神经元；这只是一个高度简化的模型。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麦卡洛</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">克</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和皮茨所展示的是，原则上，神经网络可以计算数字计算机所能计算的任何函数。结果是更多的神经科学，而不是计算机科学：重点是要表明人脑可以被认为是一个计算设备。当科学帮助我们更好地了解自己并允许我们将这种理解应用于工程和机械时，科学通常就最引人入胜，反之亦然。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">【</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">赫布学习理论</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">】</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">唐纳德</span><span style="font-family: 楷体;">·赫布（Donald O. Hebb，1904</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">.</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">7</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">.</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">22-1985</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">.</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">8</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">.</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">20）是一位加拿大心理学家，在神经心理学领域颇具影响力，他试图了解神经元的功能如何促进诸如学习之类的心理过程。 他以赫布学习的理论而闻名，被描述为神经心理学和神经网络之父。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><img width="293" height="301" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;"> </span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">3 </span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">唐纳德</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·赫布</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">1949</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，时任麦吉尔大学教授的加拿大心理学家唐纳德·赫布发表了</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">题为</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">行为的组织</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">. </span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经心理学理论</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一书（参考资料</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">[2]</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。这项工作包含了第一个明确的关于突触修饰的生理学学习规则的陈述，被称为</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“赫布突触”。他的理论被称为赫布理论、赫布规则、赫布假设和细胞组装理论。遵循这一理论的模型，被</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">称</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“赫布学习”。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">赫布</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">理论</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">通常被解释为</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“一起发射的神经元连接在一起”，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">赫布的大脑工作模型不仅影响了心理学家理解大脑中刺激的处理方式，而且为创造模拟活体神经系统生物过程的计算机开辟了道路。虽然神经系统中突触传递的主要形式后来被发现是化学的，但现代人工神经网络仍然是以通过电脉冲传递信号为基础的，这是依据赫比理论</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">最初设计。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">赫布规则是一种描述神经元活动如何影响神经元之间联系的学习规则，即突触可塑性。赫布提出了一种神经网络中神经元连接权值的更新算法。赫布规则提供了一个简单的基于生理学的模型来模拟突触可塑性的活动依赖性特征，在人工神经网络领域得到了广泛的应用。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经元间连接的权重是神经元活动的函数。经典的赫布规则指出</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“神经元一起发射，一起连接”。在赫布规则的最简单形式，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">对于每个输入向量，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">S</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（输入向量）：</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">t</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（目标输出对），重复步骤</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">3-5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">3.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">激活输入单</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">元</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">利用输入向量</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">X</span></span><sub><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: sub;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">i</span></span></sub><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"> <span style="font-family: Arial;">= S</span></span><sub><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: sub;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">i</span></span></sub><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">i = 1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">到</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">4.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">将相应的输出值，设置为输出神经元，即</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">y = t</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，通过对所有</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">i = 1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">到</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">应用赫布规则来更新权重和偏差：</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><img width="202" height="34" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><img width="184" height="34" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">由唐纳德</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·赫布提出</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">赫布学习规则</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是神经网络中第一个也是最简单的学习规则之一，用于模式分类。它是一个单层神经网络，即它具有一个输入层和一个输出层。输入层可以有许多单</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">元</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，输出层只有一个单</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">元</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。赫布学习规则规则通过为每个训练样本更新神经网络中神经元之间的权重来起作用。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">赫布</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">规则被</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">用于执行模式关联</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">任务。赫布规则的应用可以在输入层和目标输出层组成的异联前馈神经网络中计算最优权值矩阵，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">至今仍然作为人工神经网络技术，被研究和应用。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">赫布</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">规则算法示例见附录。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">【</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">结语】</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">众所周知，今天的人工智能繁荣是由深度学习技术突破造就的。而在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2017</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">MIT</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">新闻网站的一篇介绍神经网络深度学习的文章中称，“事实上，深度学习是一种人工智能方法的新名称，称为神经网络，这种方法已经流行了</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">70</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">多年”（参考资料</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">[</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">3</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">]</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的确，</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在过去的</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">0</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年里，表现最好的人工智能系统</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">——比如智能手机上的语音识别器或</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">语言</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">自动翻译都是由深度学习技术产生的。</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">而</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">被称为</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“深度学习”的</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">基础的神经网络，有</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">70</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">多年的发展历程</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="color: #FF0000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">当然，不能把今天的深度学习视同于传统的神经网络。但是，无论如何，今天深度学习的繁荣，并非一蹴而就</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">——人工智能有过寒冬，神经网络经历过曲折，得益于科学家的坚持不懈的努力和计算机技术不断进步。这些在以后的“漫谈”博客中会进一步讨论。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参考资料：</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255);
